provisions.content:
_In this Ordinance, unless there is anything repugnant in the subject or
context,__
(1) ‘Academic Board’ means the Academic Board of the College;
(2) ‘College’ means the Military College of Engineering, Risalpur;
(3) ‘Commandant’ means the Commandant of the College;
(4) ‘Controlling Authority’ means the Controlling Authority of the College.
